data.description: Welcome to Your Dream Home in the Gated Spring Ridge Community! The search for your perfect home ends here! Step into this stunning 2021 built 2-story residence featuring 5 bedrooms and 3.5 baths, nestled in the exclusive Spring Ridge community. Located in the gated Spring Ridge community that is very convenient to shopping, medical facilities, FL-50, and the Suncoast Parkway. Walking distance to your local schools. Community includes Pool, Clubhouse, and Fitness Center. Positioned in a cul-de-sac near the community entrance for easy access and a sense of tranquility. Embrace the open, split-bedroom floor plan with the primary bedroom conveniently located on the first level. Indulge in the expansive master bathroom and walk-in closet for a touch of elegance. The kitchen boasts beautiful wood cabinets, granite countertops, and stainless-steel appliances for a stylish and functional space. Relax in the very spacious backyard, enclosed by vinyl fencing, ensuring your privacy. Enter the home through the 2-car garage with direct access to the kitchen for added convenience. Ascend the stairs to a versatile space perfect for a den or additional furniture. Less than 15 minutes to Weeki-Wachee Springs State Park. Hop on the Suncoast Parkway and be in Downtown Tampa and the airport in less than an hour. Be in Orlando on FL-50 in 1.5 hour.
